WEBVTT

00:00:06.016 --> 00:00:10.400
=The Queen of Attack=

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:13.324
=Episode 21=

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:15.000
I suddenly realize

00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:17.840
that if you were pregnant
with Xiao Xian's child

00:00:17.840 --> 00:00:19.120
and claimed it's Prince Rui's...

00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:20.040
Your Highness,

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:20.896
you...

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:22.440
You're insane.

00:00:22.680 --> 00:00:24.840
Then why not just make
Xiao Xian the heir?

00:00:24.840 --> 00:00:25.440
No!

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:26.480
On what grounds?

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:28.240
If he inherits the title,

00:00:28.840 --> 00:00:30.920
his lowborn father

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:32.280
would move into the mansion.

00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:34.880
He'd strut around looking down on me.

00:00:35.720 --> 00:00:36.680
He doesn't deserve that.

00:00:39.240 --> 00:00:40.280
Xiao Xian

00:00:40.520 --> 00:00:43.040
will never inherit the throne.

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:44.120
As for you,

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:46.600
I have my own plans.

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:49.560
Perhaps you aren't fully aware

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:52.480
of the true identity of the monster

00:00:52.720 --> 00:00:54.600
who bit you in the death cell.

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:19.120
To captivate a man,

00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:20.720
you should use the left one.

00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:24.200
Master,

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:25.960
why are you here?

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:32.800
You're my disciple.

00:01:33.360 --> 00:01:34.520
I didn't teach you properly

00:01:34.800 --> 00:01:36.080
about these incenses.

00:01:39.160 --> 00:01:40.080
Aphrodisiac incenses.

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:41.960
I never thought we'd use them.

00:01:42.760 --> 00:01:43.800
But since you need it,

00:01:44.440 --> 00:01:45.560
learn thoroughly.

00:01:46.040 --> 00:01:47.120
There's no need.

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.000
This one suits you best.

00:01:52.720 --> 00:01:54.120
It truly kindles desire

00:01:54.440 --> 00:01:55.760
by awakening buried feelings.

00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:58.200
If you feel nothing,

00:01:58.360 --> 00:01:59.760
it remains powerless.

00:02:00.160 --> 00:02:01.400
But if feelings exist,

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:03.800
you'll lose self-control.

00:02:08.600 --> 00:02:09.400
Master,

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:11.920
why are you lighting it?

00:02:12.320 --> 00:02:14.040
We've always been open with each other.

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:15.160
Why afraid?

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:27.360
What are you afraid of?

00:02:29.320 --> 00:02:30.240
You.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:32.400
Master.

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:48.200
Linlang.

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:53.120
Do you truly know yourself?

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:58.840
Let's use this incense
to reveal your true heart.

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:04.520
He's here.

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:10.400
Who is there?

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:14.800
I'm sleeping.

00:03:16.320 --> 00:03:17.280
Why are you here?

00:03:18.440 --> 00:03:19.040
Your Highness.

00:03:19.720 --> 00:03:20.320
From now on,

00:03:21.200 --> 00:03:22.560
I'll be your Mother Consort.

00:03:26.160 --> 00:03:26.840
Mother Consort?

00:03:27.360 --> 00:03:28.720
Why did you come suddenly?

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:34.760
I heard the County Princess
gave you trouble today.

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:36.480
She lured you here?

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:37.720
Why would she do that?

00:03:37.720 --> 00:03:38.400
She wants...

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:39.360
Wants what?

00:03:40.120 --> 00:03:40.800
Never mind.

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:42.200
You should leave.

00:03:49.880 --> 00:03:51.880
I know exactly
what the County Princess intends.

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:54.040
She's hated my father since young.

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:56.560
Their feud has lasted a lifetime.

00:03:57.040 --> 00:03:58.680
Even with the vilest methods,

00:03:59.240 --> 00:04:00.760
she'll never let me inherit the title.

00:04:02.480 --> 00:04:03.480
She even wants us to...

00:04:03.480 --> 00:04:04.320
Shut your mouth.

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:07.040
The incense.

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:09.880
Don't move.

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:12.360
I won't do anything to you.

00:04:13.640 --> 00:04:14.480
Remember.

00:04:14.880 --> 00:04:16.240
Whatever threats she makes,

00:04:16.240 --> 00:04:17.320
don't yield.

00:04:17.960 --> 00:04:18.880
Don't act recklessly.

00:04:21.080 --> 00:04:22.480
I've already owed you too much.

00:04:23.320 --> 00:04:24.000
From now on,

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:26.320
leave it to me.

00:04:30.640 --> 00:04:31.480
Absolutely not.

00:04:33.760 --> 00:04:34.640
You said it yourself.

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:36.680
She ordered me to come tonight,

00:04:36.680 --> 00:04:38.000
so there must be guard outside.

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:49.720
If I stay here overnight,

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:50.960
you can report success.

00:04:51.120 --> 00:04:52.440
If she threatens you again,

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:53.840
you'll have a proper excuse.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:56.040
Watch out!

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:00.760
What are you...

00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:03.720
I can't stay awake all night,

00:05:04.200 --> 00:05:04.760
right?

00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:06.040
Move.

00:05:09.400 --> 00:05:13.240
S-So you're not worried about me?

00:05:13.240 --> 00:05:15.240
I have bigger concerns.

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:31.680
What's wrong?

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:34.640
Go extinguish the candles.

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:37.440
Okay.

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:50.080
What's wrong?

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:18.080
Last night, you lit incense.

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.880
But you showed no feelings toward him.

00:06:20.200 --> 00:06:21.040
Do you understand

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:22.280
your heart now?

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.160
And what about your heart,

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:25.760
Master?

00:06:26.480 --> 00:06:31.120
You've always stayed by my side,
protecting me.

00:06:33.760 --> 00:06:34.480
Master.

00:06:38.280 --> 00:06:39.240
Master.

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:43.040
Do you want me?

00:06:59.120 --> 00:06:59.920
What's wrong?

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:04.840
You know what I desire most.

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:08.320
All my enemies have received
their due punishments.

00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:09.480
But what about me?

00:07:10.360 --> 00:07:12.360
Why can't I just be Lin Hong'er?

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:15.360
Why must I never be Lin Hong'er again?

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:18.280
Because you refuse to testify for me.

00:07:19.800 --> 00:07:21.640
Because of your secrets from the past,

00:07:21.880 --> 00:07:24.240
you can't let anyone know
you can cure Gu poison.

00:07:24.520 --> 00:07:25.280
Because

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:29.920
you were the first one poisoned.

00:07:32.360 --> 00:07:33.640
Your face changed.

00:07:34.360 --> 00:07:36.280
You can't let anyone discover

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:39.840
that the old version of you still lives.

00:07:40.600 --> 00:07:41.720
You investigated me?

00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:56.320
Master,

00:07:56.840 --> 00:07:58.360
I'm someone who returned from death.

00:08:00.400 --> 00:08:03.760
I've long abandoned hope
for love or affection.

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:08.080
Gratitude and loyalty must stay buried
in my heart for now.

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:11.360
Because I have
greater unfinished business.

00:08:12.040 --> 00:08:13.840
You taught me so much.

00:08:14.440 --> 00:08:16.520
I've schemed and strategized
every step of the way.

00:08:16.720 --> 00:08:19.040
How could I let
the County Princess threaten me?

00:08:19.320 --> 00:08:20.920
I can agree to your terms,

00:08:22.880 --> 00:08:24.520
but I have my own conditions.

00:08:25.200 --> 00:08:26.160
Conditions?

00:08:26.520 --> 00:08:27.280
Your Highness,

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:30.880
you weren't surprised at all
by my changed appearance.

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:34.280
Nor were you shocked
by the existence of that monster.

00:08:34.840 --> 00:08:37.440
Because you already knew.

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:39.920
You knew his grotesque form
was due to Gu poison,

00:08:39.920 --> 00:08:43.000
rotting his flesh
into that monstrous shape.

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:44.720
And you also knew

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:47.280
that curing this poison

00:08:47.840 --> 00:08:51.440
would permanently
alter one's appearance.

00:08:52.520 --> 00:08:53.840
So, Your Highness,

00:08:54.760 --> 00:08:56.240
you can verify

00:08:56.760 --> 00:09:00.640
and confirm my identity.

00:09:00.800 --> 00:09:03.040
I do know about Gu poison,

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:06.160
and I can help prove

00:09:06.160 --> 00:09:09.520
that this poison
drastically alters one's looks.

00:09:10.720 --> 00:09:12.560
I can even restore

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:14.320
your original face.

00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:19.400
But first, I must meet the one
who cured you.

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:24.240
I swapped the incense.

00:09:24.920 --> 00:09:28.640
It drains internal energy.

00:09:32.520 --> 00:09:34.440
Master, you refuse to testify for me.

00:09:35.240 --> 00:09:36.440
Yet in this world,

00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:39.560
you're the only one
who can prove my innocence.

00:09:40.160 --> 00:09:42.400
This matters to me more than anything.

00:09:44.400 --> 00:09:46.400
The injustice Lin Hong'er suffered...

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:52.760
I'll clear it myself as Lin Hong'er.

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:57.040
Master,

00:09:57.400 --> 00:09:58.520
as you said,

00:09:58.680 --> 00:10:00.160
this game

00:10:01.080 --> 00:10:02.800
will only grow more thrilling.

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:26.840
Can you truly change my face back?

00:10:29.440 --> 00:10:30.240
Rest assured.

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:32.720
Shentu Yu suppressed the poison for you,

00:10:32.960 --> 00:10:34.920
but he can't cure it.

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:39.200
Only I possess the antidote,

00:10:40.840 --> 00:10:42.160
because this poison

00:10:43.640 --> 00:10:45.400
was brewed by me.

00:10:57.560 --> 00:11:00.880
This needle will block his Qi and blood,

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:03.240
slow his reflexes,

00:11:04.280 --> 00:11:05.640
and cloud his mind.

00:11:07.280 --> 00:11:08.400
That way,

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:11.880
extracting answers from him
will be easier.

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:26.560
Truly, a master's excellence
shapes the disciple.

00:11:28.160 --> 00:11:29.160
The problem with him

00:11:30.160 --> 00:11:31.920
is that he's too clever.

00:11:33.280 --> 00:11:34.640
If he were a bit duller,

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:37.600
things would go much smoother.

00:11:38.840 --> 00:11:39.720
Now,

00:11:40.640 --> 00:11:42.000
it's time to restore my face.

00:11:43.840 --> 00:11:44.880
Are you sure?

00:11:46.520 --> 00:11:47.760
The process

00:11:48.880 --> 00:11:50.840
is excruciating.

00:12:13.840 --> 00:12:14.560
You're back.

00:12:27.160 --> 00:12:27.720
Father?

00:12:29.280 --> 00:12:29.880
Mother?

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:34.200
Linlang?

00:12:38.400 --> 00:12:39.240
Master,

00:12:39.800 --> 00:12:41.320
the County Princess restored my face.

00:12:41.320 --> 00:12:42.080
Lin Hong'er?

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:43.680
Do you still recognize me?

00:12:43.680 --> 00:12:44.560
Master.

00:12:44.640 --> 00:12:45.400
Master.

00:12:48.840 --> 00:12:49.640
Master.

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:51.320
- Master.
- Hong'er.

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:53.480
Hong'er.

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:55.080
Hong'er.

00:12:57.680 --> 00:12:58.560
Master.

00:12:59.560 --> 00:13:00.200
It's okay.

00:13:01.320 --> 00:13:02.040
It's okay.

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:04.360
Who are you?

00:13:11.008 --> 00:13:11.600
I...

00:13:14.400 --> 00:13:15.600
I am Shentu Yu.

00:13:16.720 --> 00:13:18.000
Don't lie to me.

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:20.280
I know your heart.

00:13:20.600 --> 00:13:21.600
You love me.

00:13:22.960 --> 00:13:24.520
You've always loved me.

00:13:25.400 --> 00:13:27.080
Just tell me the truth,

00:13:27.640 --> 00:13:29.200
and we can be together.

00:13:36.720 --> 00:13:37.320
I...

00:13:41.280 --> 00:13:42.800
I am the former Crown Prince.

00:13:54.867 --> 00:14:01.203
♪Fate begins and ends, I sip the past♪

00:14:01.203 --> 00:14:06.864
♪Love and hatred flow endlessly♪

00:14:07.795 --> 00:14:15.411
♪When spring comes, I see the truth♪

00:14:15.411 --> 00:14:21.510
♪We've changed through the years♪

00:14:21.510 --> 00:14:28.179
♪Cold lamps reflect pear blossom dew♪

00:14:28.179 --> 00:14:35.859
♪Worlds change as streams run west♪

00:14:35.859 --> 00:14:42.885
♪Rains veil hills, gathering sorrows♪

00:14:42.885 --> 00:14:49.043
♪In deep courtyards, hands drift apart♪